July is a beautiful month with many colorful flowers blooming. In Beijing's National Botanical Garden, you can see various blooming flowers including lotuses, Chinese roses and crape myrtles. Check out the video to enjoy the beautiful view of blooming July. (Cover photo via CFP) (The video is shot by Zhu Yonggen and edited by Liu Haibo)) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)